{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/bcit-ci/CodeIgniter/issues/2081","repository_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/bcit-ci/CodeIgniter","labels_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/bcit-ci/CodeIgniter/issues/2081/labels{/name}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/bcit-ci/CodeIgniter/issues/2081/comments","events_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/bcit-ci/CodeIgniter/issues/2081/events","html_url":"https://github.com/bcit-ci/CodeIgniter/issues/2081","id":9373645,"node_id":"MDU6SXNzdWU5MzczNjQ1","number":2081,"title":"MySQL database backup with foreign keys","user":{"login":"jwensley2","id":379479,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjM3OTQ3OQ==","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/379479?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/jwensley2","html_url":"https://github.com/jwensley2","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jwensley2/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jwensley2/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jwensley2/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jwensley2/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jwensley2/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jwensley2/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jwensley2/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jwensley2/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jwensley2/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"labels":[{"id":140925,"node_id":"MDU6TGFiZWwxNDA5MjU=","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/bcit-ci/CodeIgniter/labels/Feature%20Request","name":"Feature Request","color":"0b02e1","default":false,"description":null}],"state":"closed","locked":false,"assignee":null,"assignees":[],"milestone":null,"comments":1,"created_at":"2012-12-18T16:50:15Z","updated_at":"2012-12-20T14:25:08Z","closed_at":"2012-12-20T14:25:08Z","author_association":"CONTRIBUTOR","type":null,"active_lock_reason":null,"sub_issues_summary":{"total":0,"completed":0,"percent_completed":0},"issue_dependencies_summary":{"blocked_by":0,"total_blocked_by":0,"blocking":0,"total_blocking":0},"body":"When using dbutil->backup() on a MySQL database that has foreign keys it causes problems when importing since the tables that the foreign keys go to may not exist yet.\n\nDoing a mysqldump or using something like sequal pro usually adds options to disable foreign key checks like.\n\n``` sql\n/*!40101 SET @OLD_CHARACTER_SET_CLIENT=@@CHARACTER_SET_CLIENT */;\n/*!40101 SET NAMES utf8 */;\n/*!40014 SET @OLD_FOREIGN_KEY_CHECKS=@@FOREIGN_KEY_CHECKS, FOREIGN_KEY_CHECKS=0 */;\n/*!40101 SET @OLD_SQL_MODE=@@SQL_MODE, SQL_MODE='NO_AUTO_VALUE_ON_ZERO' */;\n```\n\nI think it would make sense for the backup method to add this in when generating the backups.\n","closed_by":{"login":"narfbg","id":1058011,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjEwNTgwMTE=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1058011?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/narfbg","html_url":"https://github.com/narfbg","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/narfbg/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/narfbg/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/narfbg/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/narfbg/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/narfbg/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/narfbg/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/narfbg/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/narfbg/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/narfbg/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/bcit-ci/CodeIgniter/issues/2081/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/bcit-c